excerpts: You may use our Confidential Information only for the purposes of this agreement; and must keep confidential all Confidential Information except for disclosures permitted under this clause 14; and to the extent (if any) you are required to disclose any Confidential Information by Law or in accordance with the rules of an applicable stock exchange.
On the termination of this Agreement for any reason, you must return the Confidential Information and all copies of it to us.

clauses.title: Indemnity
excerpts: You indemnify and will keep us and our Affiliates indemnified against any loss, cost, expense, damage or other liability (including legal costs on a solicitor/client basis) (Loss) arising out of: your breach of this Agreement; any claim or demand against us (including for negligence) by any person other than you, which arises from or is connected with your use of the Services or Equipment.
